name: symbiota
description: This fork of the Symbiota code is actively being developed by the Biodiversity Knowledge Integration Center (BioKIC, https://github.com/BioKIC) development team at Arizona State University. Even though BioKIC code developments are regularly pushed back to this repository, we recommend that you download/fork code directly from the BioKIC/Symbiota repository (https://github.com/BioKIC/Symbiota) to ensure that you obtain the most recently code changes.
